name: Proven Lands (Canceled)
blurb: Explore a unique, vast and beautiful science-fiction sandbox survival game, procedurally generated and studded with an AI storyteller.

rewards.reward: Thanks for believing in us. Become an astronaut today and tell the others. A warm hug from us, if you ever meet us in person.

DIGITAL COPY + GAME CREDITS + TUMBLR DLC. Grab one copy of PROVEN LANDS for a platform of your choice, when it is ready for release. PROVEN LANDS will ship initially for Windows (see platforms description). A special thanks in the game's credits. Impress your friends! And, because we're so happy about our tumblr fans: If you've a tumblr blog, grab a tumblr-only item DLC. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a39, $15 or \u20ac11)

ORIGINAL GAME SOUNDTRACK + COMPANION PDF BOOK + PLANT NAME + NIGHT ITEM DLC. A download of Wrench's soundtrack and a PDF art book from Jeffrey and others. Help us with the game content and propose a name to the pool of random plant names, which is subject to our approval. Plus a suprise item DLC at the release, which will help you in the dark. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a319, $31 or \u20ac23)
BETA ACCESS. Get an early access to our beta release. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a320, $33 or \u20ac24)

BETA ACCESS + TREE NAME + PLANT DLC + DAY ITEM DLC. Get access to our beta release. Help us with the game content and propose a name to the pool of random tree names, which is subject to our approval. Plus a fancy item DLC which will help you during the day. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a329, $47 or \u20ac35)
ALPHA ACCESS. Get an early access to our alpha release. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a330, $50 or \u20ac36)

ALPHA ACCESS + POSTER + CREATURE DLC + SUIT DLC + SURVIVOR PLATE. Be part of the earlybird alpha access squad. Grab a poster. In addition, propose a name for a randomly generated long-lost survivor plate in-game, within reason. Plus, grab a special space suit and creature DLC. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a339, $63 or \u20ac47)

CARVED NAME + PLANT/CREATURE DESIGN + ITEM NAME + TOOL DLC + PROVEN LANDS CON. Impress your friends and get a name of your choice carved into a tree, a stone or painted on a wall, which is subject of our approval. Help us with the game content and design a plant or creature model with us, or propose a name to the random item names pool, which is subject to our approval as well. Plus a useful tool DLC and a free VIP ticket to all PROVEN LANDS cons; the first pre-release con will be for con backers only. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a379, $129 or \u20ac95)

FOOD/CRAFT ITEM DESIGN OR SECOND POSTER + WEAPON DLC + VILLAGE NAME. We really appreciate your help, mate. Grab a second poster or help us with the content, send us a picture and design a food or craft item with us, and in addition propose a name for a village or creature, which is subject to our approval. Plus a hot weapon DLC. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a3149, $242 or \u20ac180)

NPC DESIGN OR 3D PRINT + STORY CHARACTER + VEHICLE DLC + STATUE. Grab a 3D print of Teruo, our main character, or become part of the game story: Join the artists, send us a picture and let's talk about a randomly generated NPC you designed, which is subject to our approval. He, she or it will have things to say. Plus, live forever and help us with a story character or just name him/her after you, within reason. Plus, get your own statue in the game, named after you, if you like. Finally, an additional vehicles DLC, for backers only. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a3399, $649 or \u20ac481)

ALIEN RACE DESIGN OR SECOND 3D PRINT + EPIC ITEM DLC + BIGGER STATUE. Join the ranks and help us with an alien race design, which is subject of our approval, or grab a second 3D print of a game model, which will be revealed in a few months. And an epic item DLC awaits you. Plus, get even a bigger statue in the game, named after you. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a3799, $1,300 or \u20ac963)

NOVEL CHARACTER + THIRD 3D PRINT + PLANET NAME. Wowsome, mate! Help us with a character in the upcoming illustrated novel, even name him or her after you, within reason. We name a planet after you or a name you like, within reason as well. In addition, a 3D print of something alien-like, which will be revealed in a few months. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a31,999, $3,252 or \u20ac2,409)

GODLIKE + CONTENT WIZARD + PHAENOMENA NAME + SPECIAL 3D PRINT. This is absolutely incredible! Become a game content wizard with special Google Hangouts, and help us with the game in general. Feel free to talk to us about your ideas. If you really like the game that much, perhaps we should talk about your reward. We name a phaenomena like an ion storm after you or a name you like, within reason. In addition, a special 3D print which will be revealed in a few months. All previous rewards included. (est. \u00a34,999, $8,133 or \u20ac6,024)
